:"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"cfd9af87-0210-4934-9e04-20bc708c4206":{"value":{"id":"cfd9af87-0210-4934-9e04-20bc708c4206","version":1568,"type":"page","properties":{"title":[["小而美的网页标记插件"]]},"content":["e4bdee7a-da6d-4439-861a-9a9972ea0338","21594144-16b9-4074-a360-e481adff3c35","5cbb32ec-869f-48a2-a8f1-2fc6d3eb63ee","15c1d532-ac75-8046-8403-dd95c1b27e71","15c1d532-ac75-8014-8904-eaba7ac2d7b9","15c1d532-ac75-8003-972f-d7c7a4b6560e","15c1d532-ac75-80c5-a978-d615cc8341de","8015d13d-b6e1-468b-bde7-7f9f1cf68cab"],"format":{"site_id":"1b577656-46b9-8141-9374-0079e558d50a","page_icon":"https://pagenote.cn/images/pagenote.png","page_full_width":false,"page_small_text":true,"page_cover_position":0.5},"permissions":[{"role":"editor","type":"user_permission","user_id":"7c55490e-52d4-4bf9-8b86-dc9b51162224"},{"role":{"read_content":true},"type":"bot_permission","bot_id":"4c09af0e-92de-4e7c-81e5-c2bbfbd99cfb"},{"role":"reader","type":"public_permission","is_site":true,"added_timestamp":1662684371201,"allow_search_engine_indexing":true}],"created_time":1627521540000,"last_edited_time":1757486033806,"parent_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6","parent_table":"space","alive":true,"file_ids":["2e907910-c646-493f-84a4-a5356b71353b","eaf5230e-99f5-46c3-8c08-bb75db3f39c0"],"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6","crdt_format_version":1,"crdt_data":{"title":{"r":"bPkoDBO7FTzSxgr6u3Zqcw,\"start\",\"end\"","n":{"bPkoDBO7FTzSxgr6u3Zqcw,\"start\",\"end\"":{"s":{"x":"bPkoDBO7FTzSxgr6u3Zqcw","i":[{"t":"s"},{"t":"t","i":["jF-g9oCG1wzw",1],"o":"start","l":10,"c":"小而美的网页标记插件"},{"t":"e"}],"l":""},"c":[]}}}}},"role":"reader"},"aeb390ad-e78d-41d8-b6cb-91d8347eaf41":{"value":{"id":"aeb390ad-e78d-41d8-b6cb-91d8347eaf41","version":1136,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["很多人都在农村生活过，对农村有着深厚的感情。那里似乎是最后一片净土，总想着能够有一天衣锦还乡，回到那片地方。"]]},"created_time":1716439680607,"last_edited_time":1716440270390,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"aff597dd-ba32-4a49-bab1-3ee36f2e6db6":{"value":{"id":"aff597dd-ba32-4a49-bab1-3ee36f2e6db6","version":491,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["辞职后，回到家乡待了一段时间，又离开了它。在我看来，那是我回不去的故乡了。因为，那不是我想象的农村。"]]},"created_time":1716439871010,"last_edited_time":1716441945256,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"6fb581d2-db75-4cac-b297-3e961e688a49":{"value":{"id":"6fb581d2-db75-4cac-b297-3e961e688a49","version":776,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["最近很火的电视剧“我的阿勒泰”，很多人说很向往。可是农民不回觉得麦田浪漫，渔民也不会觉得大海浪漫，牧民更不会觉得草原浪漫。只有旁观者才会发现不深入其中的那些美。"]]},"created_time":1716541395219,"last_edited_time":1716541535224,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"9249b178-5fc5-4011-826c-5770290e2244":{"value":{"id":"9249b178-5fc5-4011-826c-5770290e2244","version":3,"type":"text","created_time":1716440286425,"last_edited_time":1716440286425,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"9790ba07-ee69-4f6a-b6aa-201e0a0770e8":{"value":{"id":"9790ba07-ee69-4f6a-b6aa-201e0a0770e8","version":51,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["不便利的生活",[["b"]]]]},"created_time":1716439971209,"last_edited_time":1716439993150,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"789554d3-1bec-405e-8fbf-9a3241d175ff":{"value":{"id":"789554d3-1bec-405e-8fbf-9a3241d175ff","version":1514,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["相比不能点外卖，不能逛商场，快递不能送达是最大的痛点。大多数人心目中的农村也并非真的与世隔离吧，能够大隐隐于市，估计是最理想的。既能远离城市的喧嚣，也能享受现代科技的便利。而我接触到的农村，就真的是深山老林，也并没有风景如画。时间久了，真的会厌倦。"]]},"created_time":1716440003028,"last_edited_time":1716440483937,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"39d86b5b-816d-4042-a858-b2295e70e00a":{"value":{"id":"39d86b5b-816d-4042-a858-b2295e70e00a","version":605,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["心目中的现代化农村，应该既有优美的环境，又能有便利的生活，除了一些旅游地能够满足这些要求外，估计很难找到了。国家的农村现代化仍然有很长的路要走。"]]},"created_time":1716441557768,"last_edited_time":1716441647555,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"4cfe97f4-996f-4af5-a682-953d5f4a0071":{"value":{"id":"4cfe97f4-996f-4af5-a682-953d5f4a0071","version":3,"type":"text","created_time":1716440041148,"last_edited_time":1716440041148,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"15a792a2-7bd2-4e45-95cf-76e284d0482a":{"value":{"id":"15a792a2-7bd2-4e45-95cf-76e284d0482a","version":109,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["农村也有自己的潜规则",[["b"]]]]},"created_time":1716440041037,"last_edited_time":1716440053740,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"9309bef7-c653-4365-8f28-c39b41013e44":{"value":{"id":"9309bef7-c653-4365-8f28-c39b41013e44","version":1112,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["有人的地方就有江湖，回到农村也不是逃离纷争的好办法。"]]},"created_time":1716440055127,"last_edited_time":1716442070305,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"6f5df244-10c6-443d-9906-81bc4ea244f9":{"value":{"id":"6f5df244-10c6-443d-9906-81bc4ea244f9","version":373,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["我与父母谈到，在外面，我不需要讨好我的领导；办什么事，网上办理，根据规则来就好。大多数情况下规则都是明朗的，那些需要潜规则的地方，可能我们还没有到能接触的阶段。所以，生活起来会比较自由，洒脱。"]]},"created_time":1716440659121,"last_edited_time":1716444667208,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"e83467d4-961d-4fce-a062-acfa705a0282":{"value":{"id":"e83467d4-961d-4fce-a062-acfa705a0282","version":3,"type":"text","created_time":1716441007395,"last_edited_time":1716441007395,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"cf57fc5b-dd20-4590-a8b8-b02b5a1011aa":{"value":{"id":"cf57fc5b-dd20-4590-a8b8-b02b5a1011aa","version":1705,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["而在农村，需要请村里的领导吃饭，需要维护关系。可怕之处在于，并非要向他们求什么，只是在于怕被穿小鞋，怕闹僵。越小的社区，灰色地带就越多，官大一级压死人体现得也就越淋漓尽致。我只想安静的待在自己的小家，而家里人会说，“你现在出息了，他们看的都是你的面子，这些事你得做”。无法反驳，但只知道，心里一百个不愿意。"]]},"created_time":1716440737314,"last_edited_time":1716441076019,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"22d0b5bf-7a02-4e44-b390-dca8a1aae707":{"value":{"id":"22d0b5bf-7a02-4e44-b390-dca8a1aae707","version":3,"type":"text","created_time":1716440649607,"last_edited_time":1716440649607,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"95079c41-2b65-4e6d-94f7-ff0f4b0c61ab":{"value":{"id":"95079c41-2b65-4e6d-94f7-ff0f4b0c61ab","version":1083,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["是待过了一段时间，才知道土地虽然分给了每户，但也不是能够随心所欲地使用的。想把家门口的一块地做成花园、院子？不行！甚至种哪类农作物也有规定，因为村里有统一的发苗、施肥、售卖。不按要求种荒着行不行？不行，不种就得让别人种。多数人心中的打造一个”梦中情园”也不是一件简单的事。"]]},"created_time":1716440523854,"last_edited_time":1716441729986,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"e43c36e6-3d95-4a04-bd1b-322941322395":{"value":{"id":"e43c36e6-3d95-4a04-bd1b-322941322395","version":3,"type":"text","created_time":1716440003157,"last_edited_time":1716440003157,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"ea048a6f-b826-4db9-aae6-53b907b6c448":{"value":{"id":"ea048a6f-b826-4db9-aae6-53b907b6c448","version":138,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["无法与上一代共处",[["b"]]]]},"created_time":1716439993736,"last_edited_time":1716440507955,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"a2acf010-6667-4389-ac31-3386d6c548b3":{"value":{"id":"a2acf010-6667-4389-ac31-3386d6c548b3","version":1056,"type":"text","properties":{"title":[["家可以长回，但不能久待，是多少年轻人的真实写照。改变别人比改变自己难太多了，两代人的观念在相处的每一天都在发生碰撞，冲突也是必然。相比回到家乡寻找一片净土，逃离城市、逃离家乡，寻找自己的第二故乡似乎是更好的一种解法。"]]},"created_time":1716440019334,"last_edited_time":1716441924283,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"},"b7ae73fa-e23c-4864-9a44-d7a6296b80cc":{"value":{"id":"b7ae73fa-e23c-4864-9a44-d7a6296b80cc","version":3,"type":"text","created_time":1716441952726,"last_edited_time":1716441952726,"parent_id":"b0571a3f-f114-49be-b697-5843e40efcb5","parent_table":"block","alive":true,"space_id":"c9077656-46b9-4ba8-89b0-0bc21f118ff6"},"role":"reader"}},"collection":{"d093839d-1d66-4880-811c-bb060627dd5d":{"value":{"id":"d093839d-1d66-4880-811c-bb060627dd5d","version":231,"name":[["博文"]],"schema":{"IxS`":{"name":"推荐","type":"select","options":[{"id":"F<dv","color":"brown","value":"🌟🌟🌟🌟","collectionIds":["d093839d-1d66-4880-811c-bb060627dd5d"]},{"id":"v}gt","color":"default","value":"🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟","collectionIds":["d093839d-1d66-4880-811c-bb060627dd5d"]},{"id":"{SbB","color":"green","value":"🌟🌟🌟","collectionIds":["d093839d-1d66-4880-811c-bb060627dd5d"]},{"id":"zwLq","color":"default","value":"🌟🌟","